<ptxt>EXAMPLE:</ptxt>
<ptxt>The 5.340 mm (0.2102 in.) lifter is installed, and the measured clearance is 0.430 mm (0.0169 in.). Replace the 5.340 mm (0.2102 in.) lifter with a new No. 42 lifter.</ptxt>
